Using shared store
```ts
scenario("Store Example")
  .setup((ctx) => {
    ctx.store.set("startTime", Date.now());
  })
  .step("Check duration", (ctx) => {
    const start = ctx.store.get("startTime") as number;
    console.log(`Elapsed: ${Date.now() - start}ms`);
  })
  .build();
```

